38-1153.Dentist and Dental Hygienist Compact; compact privilege to practice.

A person holding a compact privilege to practice in Nebraska under the Dentist and Dental Hygienist Compact may engage in the practice of dentistry or dental hygiene as authorized pursuant to such compact.

SourceLaws 2025, LB148, ยง 4.Operative Date: January 1, 2026
